snippet.title: Tibees
snippet.description:
Hi, I'm Toby, on my channel you can expect to see videos about physics, math, astronomy and the history of science. 

If you like my channel then please help me out by sharing one of my videos with a friend. You can also support me through Patreon or Ko-fi (links below). I really appreciate it :)

Please visit my website for FAQs and contact information https://tobyhendy.com/

Thanks for stopping by and I hope you have a |mathematical| day :)


The email listed below is the address of my agent who negotiates sponsorships on my behalf. Please use this address for sponsorship matters only, for everything else please visit the contact page on my website.
